Daniel (12-FEB-2019): 
I increased the memory limit from 2024Mb to 32000MB by
  sed -i 's/-memory\\:2024/-memory\\:32000/g' config/*.epf
and I increased the time limit from 2s to 1000s with
  sed -i 's/-t\\:2000/-t\\:1000000/g' config/*.epf

